Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.42,0:22:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是那个女人贝鲁巴奥鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.79,0:22:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
